            <title>[OAK-1466] Document _modCount not monotonic increasing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1466</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The _modCount of a document may get decremented when a commit is rolled back.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
